{
  // A search-tree node — a kernel Thought carrying its MCTS stats as typed facts: `visits`/`wins`
  // (the driver backpropagates), `move` (the action that produced it), `parent` (the edge). 0 is a
  // valid visits value (require = resolvability, not truthiness). Named SearchNode, not "Node":
  // Node/Segment are the pre-set ROOT FACTS one anchors on via `require` (the Vertice/Edge
  // pattern); a conditioned concept NAMED like a root fact maps before its requires resolve and
  // its children are never descended (the linted `engine-marker-name` trap).
  "require": ["Thought", "visits"]
}
